1)app is rendered using ReactDOM...see index.js :
const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'));
root.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <App />
  </React.StrictMode>
  
  2)where is it rendered?...see index.html:
  <div id="root"></div>
  above is root DOM node
  
  
